<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-06-0769 </DOCNO><TEXT>This book is an appraisal of the UN Conference on New and Renewable Sourcesof Energy, held in Nairobi in 1981. It examines the technological andeconomic prospects and the problems involved in application of new andrenewable energy technologies for development. It provides a summaryof international thinking and action on the development of alternativeenergy sources.</TEXT></DOC>